Package: mfmsbm
Title: Collapsed Gibbs Sampler for Mixture of Finite Mixtures of Stochastic Block Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Michele", "Chinì", , "michele.chini@edu.unito.it", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Implements a collapsed Gibbs sampler for Bayesian community detection
    in networks using Mixture of Finite Mixtures of Stochastic Block Models (MFM-SBM).
    Supports both zero-truncated Poisson and Gnedin priors on the number of components.
    Includes functions for network generation, post-processing of MCMC output,
    sensitivity analysis, and convergence diagnostics. Based on the methodology
    described in Geng et al. (2019) <doi:10.1080/01621459.2018.1458618>.
